sequenceDiagram
    participant Person as "Student"
    participant Front as "Browser"
    participant Back as "PHP Backend"
    participant DB as "MySQL"

    Person->>Front: Fill & submit project form
    Front->>Back: POST /index.php?route=submit
    Back->>DB: INSERT INTO projects
    DB->>Back: project_id
    Back->>Back: trigger Notifier (n8n webhook)
    Back->>Front: redirect to dashboard
    Front->>Person: Success message